entry.value: -- Insert or update the "shapes" table WITH shape_insert AS ( INSERT INTO shapes (name) VALUES ('${shape}') ON CONFLICT (name) DO NOTHING RETURNING id ), -- Insert or update the "countries" table country_insert AS ( INSERT INTO countries (name) VALUES ('${country}') ON CONFLICT (name) DO NOTHING RETURNING id ), -- Insert or update the "states" table state_id AS ( SELECT id FROM states WHERE name = '${state}' ) -- Finally, insert into the "reports" table using the retrieved IDs INSERT INTO reports (event_date, shape_id, country_id, state_id) SELECT '${event_date}', COALESCE((SELECT id FROM shape_insert), (SELECT id FROM shapes WHERE name = '${shape}')), COALESCE((SELECT id FROM country_insert), (SELECT id FROM countries WHERE name = '${country}')), (SELECT id FROM state_id)

INSERT INTO states (name) VALUES ('AL'), -- Alabama ('AK'), -- Alaska ('AZ'), -- Arizona ('AR'), -- Arkansas ('CA'), -- California ('CO'), -- Colorado ('CT'), -- Connecticut ('DE'), -- Delaware ('FL'), -- Florida ('GA'), -- Georgia ('HI'), -- Hawaii ('ID'), -- Idaho ('IL'), -- Illinois ('IN'), -- Indiana ('IA'), -- Iowa ('KS'), -- Kansas ('KY'), -- Kentucky ('LA'), -- Louisiana ('ME'), -- Maine ('MD'), -- Maryland ('MA'), -- Massachusetts ('MI'), -- Michigan ('MN'), -- Minnesota ('MS'), -- Mississippi ('MO'), -- Missouri ('MT'), -- Montana ('NE'), -- Nebraska ('NV'), -- Nevada ('NH'), -- New Hampshire ('NJ'), -- New Jersey ('NM'), -- New Mexico ('NY'), -- New York ('NC'), -- North Carolina ('ND'), -- North Dakota ('OH'), -- Ohio ('OK'), -- Oklahoma ('OR'), -- Oregon ('PA'), -- Pennsylvania ('RI'), -- Rhode Island ('SC'), -- South Carolina ('SD'), -- South Dakota ('TN'), -- Tennessee ('TX'), -- Texas ('UT'), -- Utah ('VT'), -- Vermont ('VA'), -- Virginia ('WA'), -- Washington ('WV'), -- West Virginia ('WI'), -- Wisconsin ('WY'); -- Wyoming
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS reports ( id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, event_date TIMESTAMP, shape_id INT, country_id INT, state_id INT );
